<i>Look down, look down</i>

16
00:02:42,560 --> 00:02:46,087
<i>They've all forgotten you</i>

17
00:02:46,160 --> 00:02:47,525
<i>When I get free</i>

18
00:02:47,600 --> 00:02:50,604
<i>You won't see me here for dust!</i>

19
