22
00:02:58,760 --> 00:03:01,604
<i>Look down, look down</i>

23
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:05,606
<i>You're standing in your grave</i>

24
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:12,044
Retrieve the flag.

25
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,169
<i>Now, Prisoner 24601</i>

26
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:05,769
<i>Your time is up
And your parole's begun</i>

27
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:07,683
<i>You know what that means?</i>

28
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:10,764
<i>Yes. It means I'm free</i>

29
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:14,690
<i>No. Follow to the letter
Your itinerary</i>

30
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:17,445
<i>This badge of shame
You'll show it till you die</i>

31
00:04:17,520 --> 00:04:19,921
<i>It warns you're a dangerous man</i>

32
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:22,970
<i>I stole a loaf of bread</i>

33
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:27,570
<i>My sister's child
was close to death</i>

34
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:28,766
<i>And we were starving</i>

35
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:30,086
<i>You will starve again</i>

36
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:33,209
<i>Unless you learn
the meaning of the law</i>

37
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:36,922
<i>I know the meaning
of those 19 years</i>

38
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:41,369
<i>A slave of the law!</i>

39
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:44,850
<i>Five years for what you did</i>

40
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:47,207
<i>The rest because
you tried to run</i>

41
00:04:47,640 --> 00:04:50,166
<i>Yes, 24601</i>

42
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:53,289
<i>My name is Jean Valjean!</i>

43
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:56,489
<i>And I'm Javert!</i>

44
00:04:56,560 --> 00:04:58,688
<i>Do not forget my name</i>

45
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,841
<i>Do not forget me</i>

46
00:05:02,520 --> 00:05:05,000
<i>24601</i>

47
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:09,809
<i>Look down, look down</i>

48
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:13,168
<i>You'll always be a slave</i>

49
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:16,323
<i>Look down, look down</i>

50
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:20,564
<i>You're standing in your grave</i>

51
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:47,205
<i>Freedom at last
