52
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:53,441
<i>Never forget the years,
the waste</i>

53
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:58,771
<i>Nor forgive them
for what they've done</i>

54
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:03,525
<i>They are the guilty everyone</i>

55
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:08,004
<i>The day begins
And now let's see</i>

56
00:06:08,080 --> 00:06:13,405
<i>What this new world
Will do for me</i>

57
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,685
Can I help?
A day's work?

58
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:32,761
Papers.

59
00:06:40,080 --> 00:06:42,287
No work here.

60
00:06:42,920 --> 00:06:46,288
Valjean, as a dangerous
man, you will be on parole forever.

61
