00:53:35,200 --> 00:53:36,725
<i>I found her
wandering in the wood</i>

675
00:53:36,880 --> 00:53:40,851
<i>This little child, I found
her trembling in the shadows</i>

676
00:53:41,000 --> 00:53:42,684
<i>And I am here to help Cosette</i>

677
00:53:42,840 --> 00:53:46,003
<i>I will settle any debt
you may think proper</i>

678
00:53:46,200 --> 00:53:50,728
<i>I will pay what I must pay</i>

679
00:53:51,560 --> 00:53:54,370
<i>To take Cosette away</i>

680
00:53:56,720 --> 00:53:58,051
I love you.

681
00:53:59,880 --> 00:54:02,360
<i>This is a duty I must heed</i>

682
00:54:05,600 --> 00:54:08,922
