685
00:54:22,600 --> 00:54:24,602
<i>Now your mother is with God</i>

686
00:54:28,680 --> 00:54:31,923
<i>Her suffering is over</i>

687
00:54:34,680 --> 00:54:38,765
<i>And I speak here with her voice</i>

688
00:54:40,520 --> 00:54:45,162
<i>And I stand here in her place</i>

689
00:54:47,440 --> 00:54:49,442
Come on.

690
00:54:49,640 --> 00:54:52,644
<i>And from this day, and evermore</i>

691
00:54:52,800 --> 00:54:55,087
<i>Let me take your coat, monsieur</i>

692
00:54:55,240 --> 00:54:58,289
<i>Cosette shall live
