<i>Take a chair</i>

697
00:55:07,280 --> 00:55:11,683
<i>Cosette shall have a father now</i>

698
00:55:15,520 --> 00:55:19,570
<i>What to do?
What to say?</i>

699
00:55:19,720 --> 00:55:23,645
<i>Shall you carry
our treasure away?</i>

700
