<i>What a gem!
What a pearl!</i>

701
00:55:27,720 --> 00:55:30,883
<i>Beyond rubles is
our little girl</i>

702
00:55:31,760 --> 00:55:35,446
<i>How can we talk of debt?</i>

703
00:55:35,640 --> 00:55:40,885
<i>Let's not haggle
for darling Colette</i>

704
00:55:41,040 --> 00:55:42,087
Cosette.
<i>Cosette</i>

705
00:55:43,360 --> 00:55:47,684
<i>Dear Fantine, gone to rest</i>

706
00:55:47,840 --> 00:55:50,241
<i>Have we done for her
child what is best?</i>

707
00:55:50,400 --> 00:55:51,481
I think so.

708
00:55:51,640 --> 00:55:55,486
<i>Shared our bread,
shared each bone</i>

709
00:55:55,640 --> 00:55:58,610
<i>Treated her like
she's one of our own</i>

710
00:55:58,760 --> 00:56:00,000
Yes, our own.

711
00:56:00,120 --> 00:56:01,406
<i>Like our own, monsieur!</i>

712
00:56:01,560 --> 00:56:02,721
The cost adds up.

713
00:56:02,920 --> 00:56:05,446
<i>Your feelings do
you credit, sir</i>

714
00:56:05,560 --> 00:56:08,131
<i>And I will ease
the parting blow</i>

715
00:56:08,280 --> 00:56:12,444
<i>Let us not talk of bargains
and bones and greed</i>

716
