<i>If she hadn't so often been ill</i>

719
00:56:26,120 --> 00:56:29,727
<i>Little dear, cost us dear</i>

720
00:56:29,880 --> 00:56:33,168
<i>Medicines are expensive,
monsieur</i>

721
00:56:34,480 --> 00:56:37,802
<i>Not that we begrudged a sou</i>

722
00:56:37,880 --> 00:56:40,611
<i>It's no more than
we Christians must do</i>

723
00:56:40,720 --> 00:56:43,485
