And, open.

733
00:57:16,400 --> 00:57:17,401
It's for you.

734
00:57:19,360 --> 00:57:22,011
<i>Where I go, you will be</i>

735
00:57:22,680 --> 00:57:25,843
<i>Will you be like a papa to me?</i>

736
00:57:26,640 --> 00:57:29,689
<i>Yes, Cosette This is true</i>

737
00:57:30,600 --> 00:57:33,888
