01:03:50,760 --> 01:03:56,802
<i>There, out in the darkness</i>

804
01:03:56,960 --> 01:04:00,646
<i>A fugitive running</i>

805
01:04:00,800 --> 01:04:04,247
<i>Fallen from God</i>

806
01:04:04,920 --> 01:04:08,686
<i>Fallen from grace</i>

807
01:04:08,840 --> 01:04:12,003
<i>God be my witness</i>

808
01:04:12,200 --> 01:04:15,363
<i>I never shall yield</i>

809
01:04:15,520 --> 01:04:18,569
<i>Till we come face to face</i>

810
01:04:19,160 --> 01:04:22,926
<i>Till we come face to face</i>

811
01:04:23,080 --> 01:04:25,367
<i>He knows his way in the dark</i>

812
