<i>With order and light</i>

821
01:05:04,920 --> 01:05:08,242
<i>You are the sentinels</i>

822
01:05:08,400 --> 01:05:11,051
<i>Silent and sure</i>

823
01:05:11,360 --> 01:05:13,931
<i>Keeping watch in the night</i>

