01:05:15,000 --> 01:05:18,322
<i>Keeping watch in the night</i>

825
01:05:18,720 --> 01:05:22,008
<i>You know your place in the sky</i>

826
01:05:22,160 --> 01:05:25,050
<i>You hold your course
and your aim</i>

827
01:05:25,200 --> 01:05:29,205
<i>And each in your season
returns and returns</i>

828
01:05:29,400 --> 01:05:33,086
<i>And is always the same</i>

829
01:05:33,280 --> 01:05:37,126
<i>And if you fall as Lucifer fell</i>

830
01:05:37,280 --> 01:05:41,604
<i>You fall in flames!</i>

831
01:05:41,760 --> 01:05:46,129
<i>And so it must be,
