dance Watch 'em till they drop!</i>

1820
02:20:54,400 --> 02:20:56,971
<i>Keep your wits about you
and you'll stand on top!</i>

1821
02:20:57,240 --> 02:20:59,925
<i>Masters of the land
Always get our share</i>

1822
02:21:00,080 --> 02:21:02,481
<i>Clear away the barricades
and we're still there</i>

1823
02:21:02,720 --> 02:21:05,451
<i>We know where
the wind is blowing</i>

1824
02:21:05,680 --> 02:21:07,523
<i>Money is the stuff we smell</i>

1825
02:21:08,240 --> 02:21:09,526
<i>And when we're rich as Croesus</i>

1826
02:21:09,600 --> 02:21:11,728
<i>Jesus! Won't
we see you all in hell!</i>

1827
02:21:16,520 --> 02:21:18,010
How dare you!

1828
02:21:28,800 --> 02:21:32,361
<i>Alone I wait in the shadows</i>

1829
02:21:34,000 --> 02:21:36,924
<i>I count the hours until I sleep</i>

1830
02:21:39,080 --> 02:21:43,449
<i>I dreamed a dream
Cosette stood by</i>

1831
02:21:43,640 --> 02:21:48,248
<i>It made her weep to know I die</i>

1832
02:21:52,960 --> 02:21:56,567
<i>Alone at the end of the day</i>

1833
02:21:58,560 --> 02:22:02,201
<i>Upon this wedding night I pray</i>

1834
02:22:03,840 --> 02:22:09,131
<i>Take these children, my Lord,
to Thy embrace</i>

1835
02:22:10,400 --> 02:22:17,329
<i>And show them grace</i>

1836
02:22:20,960 --> 02:22:26,763
<i>God on high</i>

1837
02:22:29,600 --> 02:22:33,730
<i>Hear my prayer</i>

1838
