<i>Will you join in our crusade?</i>

1911
02:28:37,520 --> 02:28:40,364
<i>Who will be strong
and stand with me?</i>

1912
02:28:40,520 --> 02:28:43,444
<i>Somewhere beyond the barricade</i>

1913
02:28:43,560 --> 02:28:46,291
<i>Is there a world
you long to see?</i>

1914
02:28:46,440 --> 02:28:49,364
<i>Do you hear the people sing?</i>

1915
02:28:49,560 --> 02:28:52,404
<i>Say, do you hear
the distant drums?</i>

